sections.content: The property covered under Sale Deed No. 330 of 2026, dated 28/Jan/2026, executed by Mugada Eswaramma in favour of Chulla Mangamma, towards the property admeasuring an extent of 64. Yds., comprised in survey number 129, situated in Gulla Padu Village & Grama Panchayati, Regidiamadalavalasa Mandal, within the District of Vizianagaram, registered at sub-registrar office Rajam, is bounded as follows: North by: Foundation Of Guggaragangamma South by: Rcc House Of Manapuram Sudha East by: Gravel Road West by: Foundation Of Singupurapu Venkatamma Note: Schedule property is part of Gramakantam as per recitals of the deed.
It is noted from the given documents and EC that the schedule property is not part of any active Mortgage or Lease Deed.

Note: Note: The EC has been verified and downloaded using the document number parameter, as the option to retrieve EC records using the property address is currently unavailable in the Online EC portal. Therefore, it is advisable for the F.I. to verify the same and proceed as per its internal policy. Further It is to be noted that the online EC has been verified using the key parameters, namely the Document Number, Survey Number/House Number, and Split Survey/House Number of the concerned SRO, as per the Deed. However, cross-verification across multiple SROs has not been carried out due to the AP portal’s requirement of separate passwords for each search parameter, and the OTP-based authentication mechanism makes searches across multiple SROs operationally infeasible.
